scenes.description: Calliope Mori acts out being a sushi chef for a guessing game with her Hololive EN guests.
Calliope Mori acts out being Takanashi Kiara, performing her signature 'Kiara Kick'.
Calliope Mori acts out the prompt 'The First Person to Die in a Horror Movie' as a dramatic challenge.
Calliope Mori says goodbye to her guests before transitioning to the singing portion of her concert.
Solo MC section where Calliope Mori expresses her nerves and gratitude before the performance.
